<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>VT 3D - 3D Printing & Design</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">VT 3D</div>
      <p class="tagline">3D Printing & Design</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="left">
        <h1>Building the Ultimate 3D Printing Setup</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">I'm a 3D printing enthusiast and creator, designing and sharing models on MakerWorld. Currently expanding my printer fleet with strategic gear investments.</p>

        <div class="printer-box">
          <div class="printer-name">🖨️ Bambu X1C</div>
          <div class="printer-detail">With AMS (Automated Material System)</div>
          <div class="printer-detail">High-end multicolor printing, fast and reliable</div>
        </div>

        <div class="printer-box">
          <div class="printer-name">🖨️ Bambu H2S</div>
          <div class="printer-detail">With AMS 2 Pro</div>
          <div class="printer-detail">Fast functional prints and advanced multicolor</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <div class="goal-section">
          <div class="goal-label">Next Goal</div>
          <div class="goal-title">A1 Mini</div>
          <p class="goal-description">
            My next printer: a compact, dedicated solo unit for minis, fidgets, and windowsill projects. Perfect for content creation and rapid prototyping.
          </p>
          <a href="https://makerworld.com/en/@VT_3D/upload" class="cta-button">Visit My MakerWorld</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p class="footer-text">Sharing 3D designs • Growing on MakerWorld • Building toward the X2D</p>
      <p class="footer-text">Follow the journey →</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
